            "id": "4539291",
            "title": "Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company Non-GAAP EPS of $3.14 beats by $0.16, revenue of $33.73B beats by $1B",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company <a href=\"https://pr.tsmc.com/english/news/3281\" rel=\"nofollow\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSM\" title=\"Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company Limited\">TSM</a></span></span>): Q4 Non-GAAP EPS of $3.14 <span> beats by $0.16</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $33.73B (+25.5% Y/Y) <span> beats by $1B</span>.</li>\n<li>In the fourth quarter, shipments of 3-nanometer accounted for 28% of total wafer revenue; 5-nanometer accounted for 35%; 7-nanometer accounted for 14%. Advanced technologies, defined as 7-nanometer and more advanced technologies, accounted for 77% of total wafer revenue.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
